Package com.flipkart.business

Interface GymService

public interface GymService
Interface for gym-related operations. Provides methods for booking management, retrieving gym details, and listing gyms.
Author:
Adarsh, Nitish

    • addBookings

      boolean addBookings(Bookings bookings)
      Adds a new booking to the system.
      Parameters:
      bookings - the Bookings object containing booking details
      Returns:

    • cancelBooking

      boolean cancelBooking(int bookingId)
      Cancels an existing booking based on the booking ID.
      Parameters:
      bookingId - the unique identifier of the booking to be canceled
      Returns:
      true if the booking was canceled successfully; false otherwise

    • showBookings

      List<Bookings> showBookings(int userId)

      Returns:
      a list of Bookings objects for the specified user
